info.name: Snowflake Spark Connect API
info.description:
The Snowflake Spark Connect API is a REST API that you can use to access, update, and perform certain actions on Spark Connect resource in a Snowflake database.

Contact Support:
 Name: Snowflake, Inc.
 Email: support@snowflake.com
